"Action" is, somehow...

1117
01:12:11,930 --> 01:12:14,864
...I feel a sensation of energy
which never runs out.

1118
01:12:15,446 --> 01:12:16,186
After that...

1119
01:12:16,966 --> 01:12:19,407
... "Action" has become my synonym...

1120
01:12:19,767 --> 01:12:21,118
...my trumpet...

1121
01:12:21,287 --> 01:12:22,542
...and my initial trigger.

1122
01:12:22,567 --> 01:12:24,287
Before they say
the word "Action"...

1123
01:12:24,327 --> 01:12:25,941
...I'm like all of you...

1124
01:12:25,966 --> 01:12:27,746
...I can feel afraid,
pain...

1125
01:12:28,326 --> 01:12:29,066
...and tired.

1126
01:12:30,166 --> 01:12:32,306
But as soon as I heard
the word "Action"...

1127
01:12:33,046 --> 01:12:34,564
...I will be a hero...

1128
01:12:35,446 --> 01:12:36,945
...who can do
any action...

1129
01:12:37,406 --> 01:12:38,827
...and achieve everything.

1130
01:12:43,526 --> 01:12:44,386
In the blink of an eye...

1131
01:12:45,006 --> 01:12:46,066
...decades have passed.

1132
01:12:47,366 --> 01:12:48,346
Life is like a dream.

1133
01:12:51,326 --> 01:12:53,026
But people always wake up
from a dream.

1134
01:12:53,446 --> 01:12:54,545
So, what should we do?

1135
01:12:59,886 --> 01:13:00,506
Rolling...

1136
01:13:01,326 --> 01:13:02,026
...and sleep again.

1137
01:13:04,166 --> 01:13:05,046
Jackie!

1138
01:13:06,986 --> 01:13:11,120
Jackie, don't forget
naming the panda.

1139
01:13:12,685 --> 01:13:13,265
Oh yes.

1140
01:13:14,005 --> 01:13:15,585
What's a good name?

1141
01:13:15,965 --> 01:13:17,526
Hey, help me.

1142
01:13:17,686 --> 01:13:19,426
You also gave me an idea.

1143
01:13:19,566 --> 01:13:22,626
It's easy to name a panda.

1144
01:13:23,125 --> 01:13:24,205
For example...

1145
01:13:24,645 --> 01:13:26,423
...Pingping, An'an, security...

1146
01:13:26,685 --> 01:13:28,546
...Gaogao, Xingxing, happiness...

1147
01:13:28,645 --> 01:13:30,482
...Mimi, Huhu is confused.

1148
01:13:32,365 --> 01:13:34,785
They were fast asleep
like a dazed person.

1149
01:13:35,405 --> 01:13:38,079
One we call "Mimi"
and the other one "Huhu".

1150
01:13:39,518 --> 01:13:40,978
Panda Huh.

1151
01:13:41,305 --> 01:13:42,642
Good name.

1152
01:13:50,045 --> 01:13:51,642
<i>Come on! Get out!</i>

1153
01:13:52,084 --> 01:13:53,004
<i>There!</i>

1154
01:13:54,204 --> 01:13:55,948
<i>- They are upstairs.</i>
- So noisy.

1155
01:13:56,884 --> 01:13:57,816
<i>Catch them!</i>

1156
01:13:58,085 --> 01:13:58,821
Someone's coming!

1157
01:13:58,845 --> 01:14:00,663
<i>Come on! Come on, let's go!</i>

1158
01:14:00,965 --> 01:14:03,226
There's someone here, Jackie!
Get up!

1159
01:14:03,325 --> 01:14:04,208
Someone's coming!

1160
01:14:04,365 --> 01:14:06,500
What are we waiting for? Let's go!

1161
01:14:06,524 --> 01:14:07,724
Come on, come on!

1162
01:14:14,604 --> 01:14:16,020
Don't let them get away!

1163
01:14:16,044 --> 01:14:16,886
Catch them!

1164
01:14:24,884 --> 01:14:26,460
Boss, we did it.

1165
01:14:26,484 --> 01:14:28,044
Boss, we've caught them.

1166
01:14:28,084 --> 01:14:29,644
We have to get him on board.

1167
01:14:30,004 --> 01:14:34,044
We're back and I
will talk to them.

1168
01:14:59,644 --> 01:15:00,444
Boss.

1169
01:15:01,164 --> 01:15:02,044
They are already here.

1170
01:15:02,204 --> 01:15:03,524
What about my panda?

1171
01:15:04,204 --> 01:15:06,663
He was vomiting
and don't eat anything.

1172
01:15:22,843 --> 01:15:23,618
You.

1173
01:15:25,523 --> 01:15:27,506
Take care of my panda.

1174
01:15:27,563 --> 01:15:28,323
Possible...

1175
01:15:28,723 --> 01:15:30,203
...I can let you live.

1176
01:15:32,913 --> 01:15:34,678
- Come on.
- What should we do?

1177
01:15:39,643 --> 01:15:41,522
- Meanwhile Jackie...
- Hi.

1178
01:15:42,563 --> 01:15:44,523
...stay here.

1179
01:15:44,923 --> 01:15:46,539
The ransom must be large.

1180
01:15:46,563 --> 01:15:47,963
Okay. Let's go.

1181
01:15:48,522 --> 01:15:49,350
Come on!

1182
01:15:50,282 --> 01:15:51,010
No!

1183
01:15:51,035 --> 01:15:51,770
No!

1184
01:15:51,842 --> 01:15:52,592
I will meet...

1185
01:15:52,642 --> 01:15:53,342
Stop!

1186
01:16:00,843 --> 01:16:01,463
You...

1187
01:16:06,522 --> 01:16:07,462
Throw him into the sea.

1188
01:16:08,202 --> 01:16:09,086
- Oh...
- Okay, Boss!

1189
01:16:09,282 --> 01:16:10,002
No!

1190
01:16:10,562 --> 01:16:11,162
Come on!

1191
01:16:11,522 --> 01:16:12,018
Come on!

1192
01:16:12,042 --> 01:16:13,962
Please! No!

1193
01:16:17,641 --> 01:16:18,682
Don't!

1194
01:16:26,682 --> 01:16:27,249
Come on!

1195
01:16:34,721 --> 01:16:35,444
Enter!

1196
01:16:50,881 --> 01:16:51,761
Cute Baby?

1197
01:16:52,121 --> 01:16:52,921
Cute Baby!

1198
01:16:54,401 --> 01:16:55,712
Wait a minute, Baby Gemoy.

1199
01:16:56,001 --> 01:16:57,401
I'll get you out soon.

1200
01:17:06,561 --> 01:17:07,601
CALL 911

1201
01:17:08,321 --> 01:17:09,601
Come on, come on!

1202
01:17:24,521 --> 01:17:25,743
This is your last meal.

1203
01:17:26,096 --> 01:17:26,781
Eat it.

1204
01:17:27,147 --> 01:17:28,427
Eat and go.

1205
01:17:31,840 --> 01:17:33,190
Are you still alive?

1206
01:17:34,095 --> 01:17:35,575
What do you think?
Are you surprised?

1207
01:17:35,600 --> 01:17:36,432
Surprised.

1208
01:17:36,920 --> 01:17:38,377
Me... They both...

1209
01:17:38,401 --> 01:17:40,001
They are my best friends now.

1210
01:17:40,041 --> 01:17:40,776
Harry.

1211
01:17:40,801 --> 01:17:41,576
Roy.

1212
01:17:41,601 --> 01:17:42,698
Say hello to Jackie!

1213
01:17:43,561 --> 01:17:44,680
- Jackie.
- Jackie.

1214
01:17:48,080 --> 01:17:49,680
What is this?

1215
01:17:49,720 --> 01:17:53,080
No, no!
Perhaps!

1216
01:17:53,480 --> 01:17:54,480
I can give you money.

1217
01:17:54,508 --> 01:17:55,748
I will give...

1218
01:17:56,400 --> 01:17:57,335
Don't...

1219
01:17:57,360 --> 01:17:58,601
No... Don't...

1220
01:18:00,000 --> 01:18:01,000
No...

1221
01:18:02,320 --> 01:18:03,160
No, no!

1222
01:18:03,200 --> 01:18:04,415
Please.

1223
01:18:04,440 --> 01:18:06,703
Can I have a life jacket?

1224
01:18:06,760 --> 01:18:08,000
I give you money.

1225
01:18:08,560 --> 01:18:09,840
I give you money.

1226
01:18:11,920 --> 01:18:12,920
What do you want?

1227
01:18:15,519 --> 01:18:16,959
What do you want?!

1228
01:18:19,200 --> 01:18:20,365
Forget it!

1229
01:18:20,396 --> 01:18:21,889
Just throw me into the sea!

1230
01:18:22,290 --> 01:18:23,096
Love!

1231
01:18:23,120 --> 01:18:24,176
No love!

1232
01:18:24,200 --> 01:18:25,496
No, no.

1233
01:18:25,520 --> 01:18:27,040
We love...

1234
01:18:27,811 --> 01:18:29,134
- Jackie!
- Yes, yes!

1235
01:18:29,159 --> 01:18:29,799
Jackie.

1236
01:18:31,439 --> 01:18:33,454
Jackie. We love Jackie!

1237
01:18:33,479 --> 01:18:35,879
Geez!

1238
01:18:42,759 --> 01:18:43,559
Ahh.

1239
01:18:44,719 --> 01:18:46,754
You two, my fans?

1240
01:18:47,039 --> 01:18:47,754
Yes!

1241
01:18:47,799 --> 01:18:48,519
Show.

1242
01:18:48,559 --> 01:18:49,937
- Time to show it.
- Show me!

1243
01:18:51,879 --> 01:18:52,735
Okay, okay!

1244
01:18:52,759 --> 01:18:53,854
No, no.
I believe in you guys.

1245
01:18:53,879 --> 01:18:54,559
Sitting.

1246
01:18:54,599 --> 01:18:55,359
Okay, okay.

1247
01:18:56,399 --> 01:18:57,478
Jackie, here's the thing.

1248
01:18:58,158 --> 01:19:00,694
They kidnapped the panda
to be sold to rich businessmen.

1249
01:19:00,719 --> 01:19:03,254
But they don't know
who is this entrepreneur.

1250
01:19:03,279 --> 01:19:06,419
So, that's how this ship will be
anchored, the panda will be delivered.

1251
01:19:07,039 --> 01:19:07,919
Oh no.

1252
01:19:09,159 --> 01:19:10,214
What about Xiaozhu?

1253
01:19:10,239 --> 01:19:12,098
Find the panda and Xiaozhu soon.

1254
01:19:12,511 --> 01:19:15,532
You can make sure that
all communications are active on the island?

1255
01:19:25,272 --> 01:19:26,511
<i>We'll go first.</i>

1256
01:19:26,878 --> 01:19:27,998
<i>See you tomorrow.</i>

1257
01:19:31,838 --> 01:19:32,898
Be careful.

1258
01:19:33,697 --> 01:19:34,418
Okay!

1259
01:19:53,838 --> 01:19:54,917
<i>What are you doing?</i>

1260
01:19:55,157 --> 01:19:56,572
<i>- Stop!
- Get your hands off me!</i>

1261
01:19:56,597 --> 01:19:58,373
<i>- Just leave it!
- Take off the box!</i>

1262
01:19:58,398 --> 01:19:59,454
<i>- Stop, please.
- Go!</i>

1263
01:19:59,478 --> 01:20:00,358
<i>Take off the box!</i>

1264
01:20:00,398 --> 01:20:01,465
<i>- Go!
- Stop!</i>

1265
01:20:02,038 --> 01:20:03,118
<i>Don't touch the panda!</i>

1266
01:20:03,758 --> 01:20:04,638
Stay here.

1267
01:20:20,918 --> 01:20:22,762
- Save Xiaozhu! Quickly!
- Okay.

1268
01:20:30,437 --> 01:20:31,357
Xiao Zhu.

1269
01:20:32,197 --> 01:20:34,016
I came to save you!

1270
01:20:34,117 --> 01:20:35,357
What are you doing?

1271
01:20:35,477 --> 01:20:37,675
- Get away!
- It's me!

1272
01:20:37,700 --> 01:20:38,557
It's me!

1273
01:20:46,037 --> 01:20:47,766
CARGO

1274
01:21:07,996 --> 01:21:08,696
<i>Okay friend.</i>

1275
01:21:09,236 --> 01:21:10,356
<i>It's time to play.</i>

1276
01:21:35,796 --> 01:21:36,515
<i>Hear.</i>

1277
01:21:37,635 --> 01:21:38,451
<i>I...</i>

1278
01:21:38,475 --> 01:21:40,132
<i>...will stay
and follow the truck.</i>

1279
01:21:40,156 --> 01:21:41,436
<i>You two get out of here now.</i>

1280
01:21:41,476 --> 01:21:43,035
<i>Then call the police, okay?</i>

1281
01:21:43,436 --> 01:21:44,872
<i>You're wearing my watch, okay?</i>

1282
01:21:45,076 --> 01:21:45,852
<i>What?</i>

1283
01:21:45,876 --> 01:21:46,676
<i>Your watch?</i>

1284
01:21:52,355 --> 01:21:53,791
<i>I can't use it.</i>

1285
01:22:02,036 --> 01:22:03,196
<i>Jackie is great.</i>

1286
01:22:07,795 --> 01:22:08,494
Boss.

1287
01:22:08,955 --> 01:22:10,047
- Boss.
- Boss.

1288
01:22:10,195 --> 01:22:11,085
- Boss.
- Boss.

1289
01:22:11,155 --> 01:22:12,115
- Boss.
- Boss.

1290
01:22:15,538 --> 01:22:17,640
Friends,
Don't trust this person, okay?

1291
01:22:18,355 --> 01:22:20,961
<i>How about
Our 100 million dollars?</i>

1292
01:22:20,995 --> 01:22:22,731
<i>Already in the car, Boss.</i>

1293
01:22:22,755 --> 01:22:23,535
Continue.

1294
01:22:51,074 --> 01:22:52,612
They saw me.

1295
01:22:52,637 --> 01:22:54,314
What?
You mean the two of them?

1296
01:22:54,634 --> 01:22:56,376
It doesn't matter.
They are one of us.

1297
01:22:56,554 --> 01:22:58,760
They are one of us now.
They have defected.

1298
01:23:02,915 --> 01:23:03,924
What does it mean?

1299
01:23:03,994 --> 01:23:04,554
Oh, oh.

1300
01:23:05,154 --> 01:23:05,874
The motorbike, right?

1301
01:23:05,994 --> 01:23:07,049
- Lower your voice!
- Okay, okay!

1302
01:23:07,074 --> 01:23:08,034
What do they mean?

1303
01:23:08,074 --> 01:23:09,049
They told us to...

1304
01:23:09,074 --> 01:23:11,274
...ride a motorbike and run away.

1305
01:23:13,314 --> 01:23:14,889
Do not be afraid.
I will count to 3.

1306
01:23:14,914 --> 01:23:16,140
1, 2, 3. Run!

1307
01:23:21,634 --> 01:23:22,782
- Who's driving?
- Who's driving?

1308
01:23:24,434 --> 01:23:25,274
Hello!

1309
01:23:29,547 --> 01:23:30,296
Hello.

1310
01:23:30,754 --> 01:23:32,253
Can you ride a motorbike?

1311
01:23:37,408 --> 01:23:38,153
James!

1312
01:23:38,433 --> 01:23:39,514
The police came.

1313
01:23:42,354 --> 01:23:43,514
Take the weapon!

1314
01:23:44,114 --> 01:23:45,898
Take a defensive position!

1315
01:23:45,954 --> 01:23:46,753
Come on!

1316
01:23:47,073 --> 01:23:48,942
Hold on! Cover the exit!

1317
01:24:44,912 --> 01:24:46,712
The panda was successfully captured.

1318
01:24:51,112 --> 01:24:51,952
Wait.

1319
01:24:53,592 --> 01:24:54,741
This job...

1320
01:24:55,192 --> 01:24:57,412
...it's harder than I thought.

1321
01:24:58,152 --> 01:24:58,932
So...

1322
01:24:59,392 --> 01:25:02,242
...100 million is not enough.

1323
01:25:03,392 --> 01:25:04,952
We need more.

1324
01:25:04,992 --> 01:25:06,932
That's the price we agreed on.

1325
01:25:07,592 --> 01:25:08,332
Do not move!

1326
01:25:11,632 --> 01:25:12,672
Why are you here?

1327
01:25:13,112 --> 01:25:14,451
Give me the panda.

1328
01:25:15,177 --> 01:25:17,978
I don't want to
hurt anyone, okay?

1329
01:25:19,113 --> 01:25:19,753
Pack.

1330
01:25:20,105 --> 01:25:21,625
Sir will be home soon.

1331
01:25:27,072 --> 01:25:27,872
Wow.

1332
01:26:49,830 --> 01:26:51,605
<i>- Jackie, how are you?</i>
- I am busy.

1333
01:26:51,630 --> 01:26:52,526
You just talk.

1334
01:26:52,550 --> 01:26:54,925
<i>The police already know your location.
They are on their way there.</i>

1335
01:26:54,950 --> 01:26:56,107
- I found Baby Gemoy.
<i>- What?</i>

1336
01:26:56,749 --> 01:26:57,429
Baby Gemoy.

1337
01:26:59,510 --> 01:27:01,685
<i>- Jackie, is Baby Gemoy okay?</i>
- Caught!

1338
01:27:01,710 --> 01:27:02,910
<i>What happened to him?</i>

1339
01:27:03,270 --> 01:27:04,063
<i>Cute Baby!</i>

1340
01:27:04,270 --> 01:27:05,359
I mean me!

1341
01:27:05,430 --> 01:27:07,110
<i>That means Baby Gemoy is fine.</i>

1342
01:27:08,276 --> 01:27:10,568
<i>- Jackie, the police will be here soon.</i>
- What did you say?

1343
01:27:10,968 --> 01:27:12,688
<i>Hang in there.</i>

1344
01:27:14,189 --> 01:27:14,989
<i>Ugh...</i>

1345
01:27:15,549 --> 01:27:16,989
I can't...

1346
01:27:17,029 --> 01:27:18,589
I can't hold it in anymore.

1347
01:27:18,629 --> 01:27:19,430
<i>Why?</i>

1348
01:27:20,350 --> 01:27:22,139
<i>- Jackie!</i>
- I can't stand it...

1349
01:27:22,750 --> 01:27:25,029
<i>Jackie, just hold on a little longer!</i>

1350
01:27:30,069 --> 01:27:31,085
<i>Jackie!</i>

1351
01:27:31,109 --> 01:27:32,429
<i>Jackie, speak up!</i>

1352
01:27:32,589 --> 01:27:34,189
<i>What's wrong with you?</i>

1353
01:27:34,309 --> 01:27:35,949
<i>I'm like all of you...</i>

1354
01:27:35,989 --> 01:27:36,829
<i>...I can feel scared...</i>

1355
01:27:36,869 --> 01:27:37,935
...pain...

1356
01:27:38,349 --> 01:27:39,068
...and tired.

1357
01:27:40,241 --> 01:27:42,703
But as soon as I heard
the word "Action"...

1358
01:27:43,069 --> 01:27:44,433
...I will be a hero...

1359
01:27:45,469 --> 01:27:46,903
...who can do
any action...

1360
01:27:47,398 --> 01:27:48,649
...and achieve everything.

1361
01:27:53,109 --> 01:27:53,964
<i>Jackie!</i>

1362
01:27:53,988 --> 01:27:54,988
<i>Listen!</i>

1363
01:27:55,508 --> 01:27:56,388
<i>Action!</i>

1364
01:27:56,708 --> 01:27:57,548
<i>Action!</i>

1365
01:27:58,628 --> 01:27:59,869
<i>Action!</i>

1366
01:29:01,928 --> 01:29:03,451
- Do not move!
- Perhaps.

1367
01:29:03,708 --> 01:29:05,068
Perhaps.

1368
01:29:05,748 --> 01:29:06,389
Don't...

1369
01:29:06,947 --> 01:29:08,043
Perhaps.

1370
01:29:08,067 --> 01:29:10,442
<i>Jackie, how are you?
Are you okay?</i>

1371
01:29:10,467 --> 01:29:11,922
<i>Hello? Jackie? Jackie!</i>

1372
01:29:11,947 --> 01:29:13,323
<i>Jackie, what happened?</i>

1373
01:29:13,347 --> 01:29:16,242
<i>What happened to Baby Gemoy?
Hello, Jackie? Jackie!</i>

1374
01:29:16,267 --> 01:29:17,922
- You're so troublesome!
<i>- I know!</i>

1375
01:29:17,947 --> 01:29:20,291
<i>- Jackie, how is Baby Gemoy?</i>
- He's fine.

1376
01:29:20,800 --> 01:29:21,960
Me too.

1377
01:29:22,107 --> 01:29:23,283
Stop it.

1378
01:29:23,307 --> 01:29:25,268
- We met at the pier.
<i>- Okay! Jackie...</i>

1379
01:29:38,226 --> 01:29:39,827
Are you the one who wants pandas?

1380
01:29:41,547 --> 01:29:42,087
Why?

1381
01:30:06,272 --> 01:30:07,472
6 months ago...

1382
01:30:08,986 --> 01:30:11,626
...Pasha was diagnosed
suffering from leukemia.

